# Clinical Conventions
- FHIR first: use R4 resources and standard code systems (LOINC, SNOMED, RxNorm)
- PHI redaction at source; never log or embed PHI
- Audit trail for all create/update/delete on clinical data
- 21 CFR Part 11: electronic signatures, access controls, data integrity
- ICH E6: protocol adherence, source data verification, trial integrity
